Problem 2: Shopping Bill with Discount
Take:
• Item price
• Quantity
Calculate total amount.
Conditions:
• If total amount > 1000 AND quantity > 5 → apply 10% discount
• Otherwise normal total
Print:
• Total amount
• Discount (if any)
• Final payable amount

#! bin/bash
read -p "enter price : " price
read -p "enter quantity : " quantity
amount=$(($price*$quantity))
echo "Total amount : $amount"
if [[ $amount -gt 1000 && $quantity -gt 5 ]];
then
    echo "Discount will be applied ! "
    finalamount=$(($amount*90/100))
    echo "Amount to be paid is $finalamount"
else
    echo " Not eligible for discount"
    echo "Amount to be paid is $amount"

fi

